column5: Wawa/Chapleau...Just returned from another (one of many) incredible fly in fishing trip with Air-Dale Fishing & Hunting based out of Wawa, ON. Jenn and Martin of Air-Dale are great people, take excellent care of you, and have a number of excellent fly in lakes for Walleye and/or Northern Pike, and they are reasonable cost.
We are heading up to Apisabigo the first week in August. Have either of you two been to the lake? Was curious of the fishing and any possible maps you may have drawn up. Thanks
